		<div class="entry-content"><div id="sharetools-story" class="sharetools theme-classic sharetools-story" data-shares="email|Email,facebook|Share,twitter|Tweet,save|Save,show-all|More,ad" data-url="//boss.blogs.nytimes.com/2014/12/05/today-in-small-business-the-best-jobs-numbers-in-years/" data-title="Today in Small Business: The Best Jobs Numbers in Years?" data-description="Starbucks plans a new chain of coffee shops for those who thought Starbucks coffee was too inexpensive. Four studies show that the Affordable Care Act is working &quot;incredibly well.&quot; And here is how to deal with a toxic employee.">
				<div class="ad sharetools-inline-article-ad"></div>
				<div id="MiddleLeft" class="ad middle-left-ad nocontent robots-nocontent"></div>
				</div><div class="inlineModule"><div class="entry"><h6 class="kicker"><a href="//boss.blogs.nytimes.com/category/dashboard/">Dashboard</a></h6><p class="summary">A daily roundup of small-business developments.</p></div></div>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">Whatâs affecting me, my clients and other small-business owners today.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>The Economy</strong></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Are these the <a href="//www.nytimes.com/2014/12/06/upshot/jobs-numbers-offer-encouraging-signs-of-momentum.html">best jobs numbers in years</a>?</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Jobless <a href="//www.csmonitor.com/Business/Latest-News-Wires/2014/1204/US-jobless-claims-fall-below-300K-as-hiring-surges-video">claims fall below</a> 300,000 as hiring surges.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Small-business optimism is at its <a href="//www.gallup.com/poll/179876/small-business-optimism-highest-early-2008.aspx">highest level since</a> early 2008.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ And the reports of a <a href="//www.inc.com/jill-krasny/how-chocolate-prices-are-impacting-small-businesses.html">chocolate crisis</a> have been greatly exaggerated.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Chinaâs economy <a href="//www.marketwatch.com/story/its-official-america-is-now-no-2-2014-12-04">surpasses</a> America&#8217;s (and hereâs whatâs <a href="//qz.com/306754/heres-whats-really-scary-about-china-overtaking-america-as-the-worlds-biggest-economy/">scary</a> about that).</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Washington</strong></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Many industry groups are <a href="//thehill.com/business-a-lobbying/business-a-lobbying/225950-weary-of-obama-business-groups-look-beyond-2016#.">counting the days</a> until President Obama leaves office.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Four <a href="//nymag.com/daily/intelligencer/2014/12/4-new-studies-obamacare-working-incredibly-well.html">studies</a> show that the Affordable Care Act is working &#8220;incredibly well.&#8221; <span id="more-90622"></span></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Retail</strong></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Starbucks plans a new chain of <a href="//www.nytimes.com/2014/12/05/business/in-the-capital-of-coffee-enthusiasm-for-starbucks-upmarket-chain.html">coffee shops</a> for those who thought Starbucks coffee was too inexpensive.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Restaurant associations in New York are <a href="//www.crainsnewyork.com/article/20141204/HOSPITALITY_TOURISM/141209903/restaurant-associations-duel-for-members">dueling for</a> new members.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Sears plans to <a href="//www.cnbc.com/id/102237069">accelerate its</a> store closings.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ This gadget could <a href="//www.inc.com/associated-press/beacons-pop-up-in-stores-ahead-of-holidays.html">revolutionize</a> the in-store experience.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ A restaurant <a href="//consumerist.com/2014/12/04/l-a-restaurant-adds-gratuity-line-for-kitchen-staff-to-every-check/">adds a gratuity line</a> to every check for the kitchen staff.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Marketing</strong></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Hispanics <a href="//www.mediapost.com/publications/article/239358/hispanics-prefer-ads-in-english-shopping-on-lapto.html">prefer their ads</a> in English.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Finance</strong></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Donald Trump has <a href="//www.entrepreneur.com/article/240476?c">fired himself</a> from the crowdfunding business.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ This holiday song was <a href="//twentytwowords.com/this-holiday-song-was-made-entirely-from-the-sounds-of-office-supplies/">made entirely</a> from the sounds of office supplies.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Uber is <a href="//dealbook.nytimes.com/2014/12/04/uber-files-to-sell-1-8-billion-in-new-shares/">now valued</a> at $40 billion.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Online</strong></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Yahoo is <a href="//adage.com/article/digital/yahoo-surpass-twitter-u-s-mobile-ads/296077/">poised to surpass</a> Twitter next year to become the third-biggest American company in mobile advertising.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Management</strong></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ A <a href="//www.fastcompany.com/3039399/the-recommender/watch-this-target-manager-give-a-vein-popping-pep-talk-for-the-ages">Target manager</a> gives a vein-popping pep talk for the ages.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ In a video made in cooperation with an animal welfare group, a chicken farmer <a href="//www.wired.com/2014/12/cwif-craigwatts-perdue/">escorts</a> cameras into his broiler barns.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Two experts contend that <a href="https://hbr.org/2014/12/family-businesses-need-one-person-to-conquer-and-another-to-rule">successful family businesses</a> need one person to conquer and another to rule.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Employees</strong></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Workers <a href="//nrn.com/government/restaurant-workers-other-industry-employees-stage-minimum-wage-strikes">calling for an increase</a> in the minimum wage to $15 an hour stage strikes in more than 190 cities.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Here is how to <a href="//www.inc.com/susan-salgado/the-problem-with-skunks.html">deal with</a> a toxic employee.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Here are 14 techniques to <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/pulse/20141203203020-14611789-14-techniques-to-make-yourself-more-likable">make yourself</a> more likable.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Birth rates in the United States hit a <a href="//theweek.com/article/index/273058/speedreads-us-birth-rates-hit-record-low-in-2013">record low</a> in 2013.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Around the Country</strong></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Google <a href="//pando.com/2014/12/04/google-makes-a-120m-bet-on-la-potentially-expanding-its-presence-in-the-region-nine-fold/">makes a $120 million</a> bet on Los Angeles.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Top leaders in 17 states <a href="//online.wsj.com/articles/seventeen-states-sue-obama-over-immigration-action-1417638088">file a lawsuit</a> challenging President Obamaâs executive action on immigration.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Around the World</strong></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ President Putin thinks that small businesses <a href="//www.csmonitor.com/World/Europe/2014/1204/Can-small-business-help-Russia-bear-West-s-sanctions-Putin-hopes-so.-video">may save</a> Russia from sanctions.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Entrepreneurship</strong></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ An online <a href="//www.inc.com/will-yakowicz/few-lucky-pot-entrepreneurs-make-reality-show-call-backs.html">reality show</a> focuses on pot entrepreneurs.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ The former owner of a hypnotherapy business <a href="//www.wausaudailyherald.com/story/news/local/2014/12/03/wausau-entrepreneur-touts-new-online-security-product/19867123/">touts her</a> new online security product.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Ideas</strong></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ These smart <a href="//www.springwise.com/smart-ballet-shoes-dancers-track-performance/">ballet shoes</a> let dancers track their performance.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Opportunities</strong></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Google is working on <a href="//readwrite.com/2014/12/04/google-for-kids-search-youtube-chrome?ut">versions of its services</a> for children.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Technology</strong></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Microsoft <a href="//www.pcworld.com/article/2855024/microsoft-takes-a-bath-on-failed-nook-partnership.html#tk.rss_all">takes a bath</a> on its failed Nook partnership.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Disney <a href="//www.startribune.com/lifestyle/284757001.html">swoops into</a> the education business with âImagicademyâ apps.</p>
